#: yayforms.php:36 yayforms.php:37 yayforms.php:67 yayforms.php:78
msgid "Yay! Forms"
msgstr "Yay! Forms"

#: yayforms.php:72
msgid "Shortcode copied to clipboard!"
msgstr "¡Shortcode copiado al portapapeles!"

#: yayforms.php:75
msgid "Preview ready — click the button below to try the form."
msgstr "Vista previa lista — haz clic en el botón de abajo para probar el formulario."

#: yayforms.php:79
msgid ""
"Yay! Forms is an online form builder software featuring user-friendly design "
"and AI-driven insights, streamlining form creation and data analysis. It "
"caters to businesses seeking efficient, engaging, and intelligent form-"
"building solutions."
msgstr ""
"Yay! Forms es un creador de formularios online con un diseño amigable e "
"insights basados en IA, que agiliza la creación de formularios y el análisis "
"de datos. Pensado para empresas que buscan soluciones eficientes, atractivas "
"e inteligentes para crear formularios."

#. translators: %s: link to yayforms.com
#: yayforms.php:84
#, php-format
msgid ""
"This plugin offers a streamlined interface for generating shortcodes to "
"embed custom forms, surveys, and quizzes into your posts, pages, or widgets. "
"Requires a Yay! Forms account, available at %s."
msgstr ""
"Este plugin ofrece una interfaz simple para generar shortcodes que incrustan "
"formularios, encuestas y cuestionarios personalizados en tus entradas, "
"páginas o widgets. Requiere una cuenta de Yay! Forms, disponible en %s."

